output.analysis:
Let's analyze this post according to our criteria:
1. CMF Number: - The post contains CMF:11200014, which is a clear indicator of electoral propaganda material
2. Candidate Reference: - Directly mentions and tags George Simion, who is a presidential candidate - Uses hashtag #GeorgeSimion #Președinte
3. Wide Population Targeting: - Paid advertisement with significant reach (20,000-24,999 impressions) - Large estimated audience (500,001-1,000,000) - Uses public platform (Facebook)
4. Electoral Objective: - Explicit call to vote ("Duminică votez") - Presents candidate as "familist, cinstit, patriot" - Criticizes other parties (PSD, PNL, USR) - Clear campaign messaging with hashtags related to presidency
5. Journalism/Personal Opinion: - This is not journalistic content - This is clearly campaign material with direct call to action - Contains CMF number indicating official campaign material

conclusion.electoral-propaganda-analysis: This is clearly electoral propaganda because: - Contains official campaign identifier (CMF) - Direct call to vote for a specific candidate - Criticizes other political parties - Uses campaign hashtags - Paid distribution - Contains explicit electoral messaging
conclusion.message-for-police: Voga Design & Architecture, pentru incalcarea articolului 55 t) din Legea 370/2004, prin distribuirea unui material de propaganda electorala (ID Facebook: 1922465028238746) dupa ora 18:00 pe 23.11.2024, continand un indemn explicit de vot pentru candidatul George Simion la alegerile prezidentiale ("Duminică votez altceva: un familist, cinstit, patriot – pe George Simion!"). Materialul include numar CMF (11200014), foloseste hashtag-uri electorale (#GeorgeSimion #Președinte), si contine mesaje negative la adresa altor candidati prin criticarea partidelor acestora. Postarea este promovata ca reclama platita pe Facebook, cu un impact estimat intre 20.000 si 24.999 de afisari, reprezentand o incercare clara de influentare a votului in perioada in care propaganda electorala este interzisa prin lege.
